=== 視覺藝術考試 ===
倫敦聖三一學院與英國藝術委員會為身處英國的考生提供關於視覺藝術的評審。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Arts Award|url=https://www.artsaward.org.uk/site/?id=64%20Arts%20Award|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2017-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104112409/http://www.artsaward.org.uk/site/?id=64%20Arts%20Award|dead-url=no}}</ref>

